<span class="headers">PoP Planar Armor Stats</span>
<p>
<p>
The quest writeup for this armor <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/articles/article_page.php?article=q55&menustr=120055000000">can be found.</a> Effects on these items were added with the December 19, 2002 patch. Effects were then changed on some of these items with the January 9, 2003 patch. <b>Any items in <i>italics</i> on the lists below have NOT been reverified since the January 9, 2003 patch, so the information on them is incomplete.</font></b> Please also note that things such as required level, lore, magic, no drop status have not always been reported in, so this information will be incomplete.
</p>
<p align="center">
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/articles/article_page.php?article=g207&menustr=120055000000#plateornate">Plate: ornate molds</a> --
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/articles/article_page.php?article=g208&menustr=120055000000#plateelemental">Plate: elemental molds</a> -- 
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/articles/article_page.php?article=g210&menustr=120055000000#ornatechain">Chain: ornate chain patterns</a> -- 
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/articles/article_page.php?article=g211&menustr=120055000000#elementalchain">Chain: elemental patterns</a>
</p>
<p align="center">
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/articles/article_page.php?article=g212&menustr=120055000000#ornateleather">Leather: ornate patterns</a> -- 
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/articles/article_page.php?article=g213&menustr=120055000000#elementalleather">Leather: elemental patterns</a> --
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/articles/article_page.php?article=g214&menustr=120055000000#ornatesilk">Silk: ornate patterns</a> -- 
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/articles/article_page.php?article=g215&menustr=120055000000#elementalsilk">Silk: elemental patterns</a>
</p><p align="center">
<a href="#effects">effect/focus information </a>
</p>
<a name="ornatesilk"><h4>Silk classes - ornate ____ pattern:</h4></a>
<h5>Enchanters:</h5>
<ul> 
<li>silken augmentor's bracelet, AC 8, STA 4, CHA 3, INT 6, AGI 5, HP 35, mana 40, sv fire 3, sv cold 4, sv poison 3, effect: flowing thought II, wt 0.2, small, ENC/ALL, magic, no drop</li> 
<li>silken augmentor's shoes, AC 10, DEX 4, STA 3, HP 30, mana 45, sv disease 7, sv poison 8, ENC/ALL, lore, magic, no drop, effect: spell haste IV</li> 
<li>silken augmentor's gloves, AC 10, STR 3, DEX 4, STA 7, CHA 5, INT 6, HP 35, Mana 50, sv fire 8, sv cold 8, focus effect: insanity storm </li> 
<li>silken augmentor's sleeves, AC 11, DEX 3, STA 4, INT 6, AGI 7, HP 40, Mana 45, sv fire 5, sv disease 5, sv cold 5, effect: mana preservation IV</li> 
<li>Silken augmentor's cap, AC 11, STA 4, CHA 5, INT 8, AGI 3, HP 40, mana 50, sv fire 3, sv cold 3, sv disease 3, sv poison 6, wt 0.3, medium, ENC/ALL, effect: plainsight (worn), lore, magic, no drop, no recommended/required level at this time, no visible graphic when worn</li> 
<li>Silken augmentors pantaloons, AC 14, DEX 3, STA 6, CHA 6, INT 8, AGI 8, HP 50, mana 85, sv fire 10, sv cold 10, wt 0.7, medium, recommended level 60, lore, magic, no drop, ENC/ALL, effect: tranquility (cast time: 12.0)</li> 
<li>Silken Augmentor's Robe, AC 15, AGI 9, DEX 9, STA 9, CHA 9, INT 13, HP 80, mana 100, sv fire 15, sv cold 15, sv poison 10; recommended level 60, ENC/ALL, magic, lore, no drop, effect (right-click): shield of Maelin (cast time 6.0)</li>
</ul>
<h5>Mages:</h5>
<ul> 
<li>Elemental bracelet of the prime, AC 8, DEX 5, STA 2, INT 5, AGI 3, HP 35, mana 40, sv fire 2, sv disease 4, sv magic 4, effect: flowing thought II, MAG/ALL, magic, no drop</li> 
<li>Elemental Leggings of the Prime, AC 14, STR 4, DEX 6, STA 4, INT 7, AGI 4, HP 50, mana 85, sv disease 10, sv poison 10, wt 0.7, medium, MAG/ALL, magic, lore, no drop, recommended level 60 (Effect: Flameshield of Ro (Must Equip. Casting Time: 8.0)</li> 
<li>Elemental shroud of the prime, AC 15, STR 10, STA 10, INT 13, AGI 7, HP 80, mana 100, sv fire 12, sv magic 12, sv poison 8, sv disease 8, wt 1.0, large, MAG/ALL, lore, magic, no drop, effect (right-click): shield of Maelin (cast time 6.0)</li>
</ul>
<h5>Necromancers:</h5>
<ul> 
