<li>Vorshar's pants of the blight, AC 14, DEX 5, STA 6, CHA 5, INT 8, AGI 6, HP 50, ,ama 85, sv cold 10, sv magic 10, wt 0.7,medium, lore, magic, no drop, effect: rune of death</li> 
<li>Vorshar's Robe of the Blight, AC 15, STR5, DEX 8, STA 11, CHA 8, INT 11, AGI 5, HP 85, mana 95, sv fire 10, sv dis 10, sv cold 10, sv magic 10, wt 1.0, large, NEC/ALL, magic, lore, no drop, recommended level 60, effect (right-click): shield of Maelin (cast time 6.0)</li>
</ul>
