<a name="effects"><h4>Focus effects:</h4></a>
<h5>Effects:</h5>
<blockquote>
<p>
Aura of Bravery: +3 HP/Tick and +30 ATK. <br />
 Aura of Courage: +1 HP/Tick and +5 ATK. <br />
 Aura of Daring: +2 HP/Tick and +20 ATK <br />
 Aura of Regeneration: +3 HP/Tick (6th Signet effect) <br />
 Aura of Valor: +4 HP/Tick and +40 ATK <br />
 Avatar: +100 STR/DEX/AGI/ATK <br />
 Faerune: See Invis, Ultravision and Enduring Breath <br />
 Flowing Thought I, II, III, - X: +1 Mana/Tick for each level <br />
 Koadic&#8217;s Heightened Focus: +5 Mana/Tick <br />
 Plainsight: See Invis and Ultravision <br />
 Refreshment: +3 HP/Tick <br />
 Shield of the Arcane: +300 HP, +36 AC, +30 SvM <br />
 Shield of the Maelin: +350 HP, +39 AC, +40 SvM <br />
 Vengeance I, II, III, - X: +5 ATK for each level 
</p>
</blockquote>
<h5>Focus Effects:</h5>
<p>
<i>(Unless noted all have a Max spell level of 65 and do NOT work on Complete Healing or % based Healing spells) </i>
</p>
<blockquote>
<p>
Extended Affliction IV: Increase spell Duration by 20% (Detrimental only) <br />
 Improved Damage IV: Increase Damage by 20% (Instant detrimental only) <br />
 Improved Healing IV: Increase Healing by 20% <br />
 Inferno of Sol: Decrease spell Mana by 20% (Strike of Solusek allowed) <br />
 Mana Preservation IV: Decrease spell Mana cost by 10% <br />
 Marr&#8217;s Gift: Increase spell Healing by 25% <br />
 Preservation of Xegony: Decrease spell Mana cost by 15% <br />
 Speeding Thought: Increase spell Haste by 18% <br />
 Spell Haste IV: Increase spell Haste by 15% 
</p>
</blockquote></p><p>
